We are pet-friendly!

Here at American Avenue, we welcome and accept Section 8/Housing Vouchers in addition to market renters!

Schedule your self-tour, and apply online today or reach out and let one of our friendly and knowledgeable leasing professionals help you find your perfect home.

To qualify for an American Avenue rental property, the combined household income must be 3x the monthly rent. For Section 8 renters, we require the combined household income be 3x the residents rent responsible portion of the monthly rent.

Average combined resident score must meet minimum requirements. Guarantors (including local Housing Authorities & Voucher Programs) are accepted and must meet outlined guarantor requirements.

Additional terms and requirements apply. All applications are processed in the order in which they are completed and received. Application does not guarantee a lease.

American Avenue is an Equal Housing Lessor under the FHA. Applicable local, state and federal laws may apply. Lease terms and conditions apply. This is not an offer to rent—you must submit additional information for review and approval. Listing features may not be accurate and should be confirmed with an American Avenue leasing representative.

Avoid rental scams! American Avenue does not list homes for lease through Craigslist, Social Serve, or any other classified advertising services.
